				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/Bi%E1%BB%87t-L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem-PBU5abeflXhMMrZjEuE9Vg">Biệt Lý Nhân Phủ - 別李仁甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/author-euImnp4iLisTPNWkShmsSA">Bạch Ngọc Thiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Bi%E1%BB%87t-Tr%E1%BB%AB/poem-rxORnN14oSIgfn_lgreXrA">Biệt Trừ - 別滁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Chi%E1%BA%BFu-th%C3%A2n/poem-fz8NXCQFYBwkgAwHdsrJYg">Chiếu thân - 照身</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Di-Xu%C3%A2n-v%C4%83n-d%C6%B0-vi-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-th%E1%BB%8B-chi-du-k%C3%BD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-tam-tuy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-th%C3%B9-chi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZYnSUnffghHOS1nhXoFlgg">Di Xuân văn dư vi Phạm thị chi du ký tặng tam tuyệt, thứ vận thù chi kỳ 1 - 怡春聞予為范氏之遊寄贈三絕次韻酬之其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-V%E1%BB%8B-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-th%E1%BB%A7-tu%E1%BA%BF/poem-21VmXPdVPsi6ly5XMzphYA">Đỗ Vị trạch thủ tuế - 杜位宅守歲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khu-th%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BB%AD-tr%C3%ADch-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%C4%A9/poem-UYZ2PCa7ZvbscLZJPwZZbw">Khu thụ tử trích thương nhĩ - 驅豎子摘蒼耳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/T%E1%BA%BF-T%C3%A1o-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-ZBn9kTPVSHvL_rCbblWpgw">Tế Táo từ - 祭灶詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A0nh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i/author-ppK7YKfOyDZw9vIHLHbJVA">Phạm Thành Đại</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-Kh%C3%A2m/Thi%C3%AAn-B%C3%ACnh-s%C6%A1n/poem-CrkPNETORjAdBnI-FGBJiQ">Thiên Bình sơn - 天平山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-Kh%C3%A2m/author-2_TKpTo9LIhei08LC-iYaw">Tô Thuấn Khâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/V%C3%A2n-trung-qu%C3%A2n/poem-jQF8RblynziS-SJYRFGcsA">Vân trung quân - 雲中君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-scZUKansddTUmXJHU2hd_w">Vương thị tượng kỳ 2 - 王氏像其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
